ous and remote flight operations further. The\ndataset and the provided tools can be accessed from\nhttps://doi.org/10.1184/R1/12707963.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 14 Jul 2019 19:35:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 24 Oct 2020 04:23:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-09"}
